basic.Source: Synthetic construct(derived from WNV NS3 helicase protein)
basic.Target Organism: [Ref.18479669]Hepatitis C virus (HCV):inhibition of HCV helicase activity(IC50>500 μM);West Nile virus (WNV):inhibition of WNV helicase activity(IC50=383±12.3 μM);Japanese encephalitis virus (JEV):inhibition of JEV helicase activity(IC50=437±13.4 μM).
